      <lg type="edition">
<l>aṇittaḻai nuṭaṅka vōṭi maṇippoṟik</l>
<l>kuralaṅ kuṉṟi koḷḷu miḷaiyōḷ</l>
<l>māmakaḷ................................................</l>
<l>..........................leṉa viṉavuti kēṇī</l>
<l>veṭuppave..................................</l>
<l>.............................maintar tantai</l>
<l>yirumpaṉai yaṉṉa peruṅkai yāṉai</l>
<l>karantaiyañ ceṟuviṟ peyarkkum</l>
<l>peruntakai maṉṉarkku varaintirun taṉaṉē.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
